PUBLIC COMMENT PERIODS - PROPOSED REGULATIONS PUBLIC COMMENT PERIODS REGARDING STATE AGENCY REGULATIONS This section gives notice of public comment periods and public hearings to be held on proposed regulations.
The notice will be published once at the same time the proposed regulation is published in the Proposed Regulations section of the Virginia Register.
The notice will continue to be carried in the Calendar of Events section of the Virginia Register until the public comment period and public hearing date have passed.
