Persons required in Â§ 45.1-361.29 of the Code of Virginia to obtain a permit or permit modification shall apply to the division on the forms prescribed by the director.
All lands on which gas, oil or geophysical operations are to be conducted, including all areas proposed to be used for land application of fluids shall be included in a permit application.
